UNITED STATES No. 19-6652 Supreme Court of the United States. January 21, 2020 I dissent for the reasons set out in Brown v. United States , 586 U.S. ----, 139 S.Ct. 14, 202 L.Ed.2d 302 (2018) (Sotomayor, J., dissenting).
